#: src/Form/Admin/SearchConfigFacetFieldset.php:106
msgid ""
"#\"></a><div class=\"field-description no-link\">\n"
"- Input types may be Checkbox (default), RangeDouble, Select, SelectRange, "
"Thesaurus, Tree and specific templates for mode \"direct\" if wanted.\n"
"- For \"RangeDouble\" and \"SelectRange\", the minimum and maximum should be"
" set as \"min\" and \"max\" in \"Html attributes\", and \"step\" too. The "
"option \"first_digits\" is enabled by default to extract the year from "
"dates. Set \"first_digits = false\" in \"Options\" to disable it. Set "
"\"first_digits = 3\" to group by decade (first 3 digits), \"first_digits = "
"2\" for century, \"first_digits = 1\" for millennium.\n"
"- With type \"Thesaurus\", the option \"thesaurus\" should be set with the "
"id. It requires the module Thesaurus.\n"
